<title>BLEST BE THE TIE THAT BINDS</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hehpihna gui zawmin,
 Lungkhata ding guolin;
 Vanmi umdan gui bang zawp hi,
 Kristien umdan ahi.

[V2]
 2. Zuomang chutphah ma ah,
 Lungkhata kigawm in;
 Lungtupna leh ngaihtuohna chun,
 Siktui bang luong gawm ding.

[V3]
 3. Lungngai liengvai um leng,
 Gikpuok kidawn zang leng;
 Lalpa minin kilungsiet leng,
 Thagau vangphatna din.

[V4]
 4. Tuhin kikhen mahleng,
 Lunghel thawmhau mah leng;
 Chung thangvan gam nuom tak a chun,
 Tuibang kigawm nai tiu.</lyrics>
</song>